Ship. Midget Football Championship set for Oct. 25 0 comments 
Come out to Tiger Stadium, 3 Whitehouse Rd., on Sunday, Oct. 25 and cheer on our future all-stars in the Shippensburg Midget Football Championship. Grab a hot chocolate or your favorite food and snack provided by The Lollipop Shop and support the football players and cheerleaders as they compete. Admission and parking is free.
